file: js.json
purpose: Plover stenography dictionary mapping chord sequences to JavaScript/TypeScript code snippets. Covers control flow, variable declarations with type annotations, function definitions, and array indexing.
invariants:
  - All entries use `{^}` prefix to suppress preceding space before insertion.
  - Cursor-positioning after insertion is done exclusively via `{#Up}` and `{#Left}`/`{#Right}` key sequences.
external_deps:
functions: